Scala 3 has a new way of defining the main() method.
For example, here is a simple "Hello World" program
that works only in Scala 3.

@main def main(): Unit =
  println("Hello World.")
end main

For more info about the Scala 3 main() method, read this web page:
https://docs.scala-lang.org/scala3/book/methods-main-methods.html
